# Discord Ticket & Utility Bot

A modern Discord bot built with an advanced ticket system, admin configuration tools, and modular event handling. Designed for scalability, clean UX, and server management automation.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🎫 Advanced Ticket System
- Category-based ticket creation system
- Priority levels (Low, Medium, High)
- Private ticket channels with permission control
- Claim / Close / Transcript system
- Duplicate ticket prevention
- Anti-spam cooldown protection

### 🧭 Support Panel System
- Professional embedded ticket panel
- Dropdown category selection
- Clean SaaS-style UI
- Fully configurable panel via admin commands

### ⚙️ Admin Configuration
- `/ticket setticketchannel` command
- Configure ticket panel channel
- Configure ticket category system
- Persistent database storage

### 📄 Transcript System
- Full message history capture
- Auto-send to configured channel
- Fallback channel selection menu
- Saved preference for future transcripts

### 👋 Server Events
- Welcome & leave system (guildMemberAdd / guildMemberRemove)
- Professional embedded UI messages
- Member tracking and server stats

### 🧠 Smart Logging & Safety
- Duplicate interaction prevention
- Safe error handling
- Guild-specific configuration isolation

